  "text": "The Web-retrieval performance of our methods is substantially better than that of using only document-query similarities. The performance of our re-ranking method also transcends that of state-of-the-art methods that utilize (i) term proximity information [CITATION_1] , (ii) hyperlinks-based information, and (iii) content-based (query-independent) document quality measures [CITATION_2] . In addition, we demonstrate the merits of integrating our methods with spam detection [CITATION_3] .",
